  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bugz Bows and Curses is an incremental game disguised as a generic ​rogue-lite, complete with numbers so big they lose meaning. You play as an anti-pede with a bow, as you progress through levels, you're able to get more and more broken builds!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >> Bugz</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With an AI that reacts to what you do, running if you're strong, attacking if you're weak. Each species has its own unique and relatable personality, you will almost feel guilty killing them.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/9784e21ae30d1db6b5e4869ae27003ff.poster.avif?t=1757251247\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/9784e21ae30d1db6b5e4869ae27003ff.webm?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/9784e21ae30d1db6b5e4869ae27003ff.mp4?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >> Bows</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With tons of shops, stats, and upgrades, you'll always find a better item... even if it is just a curse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/f5460c67f76bfe5863a6d0252b2a0143.poster.avif?t=1757251247\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/f5460c67f76bfe5863a6d0252b2a0143.webm?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/f5460c67f76bfe5863a6d0252b2a0143.mp4?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >> Curses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the story story that keeps you going, and more numbers and upgrades than you need, every run comes with its own unique goal. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/b599f9990b12951272cfd6643f27a1db.poster.avif?t=1757251247\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/b599f9990b12951272cfd6643f27a1db.webm?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/b599f9990b12951272cfd6643f27a1db.mp4?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bugz Bows and Curses is an incremental game disguised as a generic ​rogue-lite, complete with numbers so big they lose meaning. You play as an anti-pede with a bow, as you progress through levels, you're able to get more and more broken builds!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >> Bugz</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With an AI that reacts to what you do, running if you're strong, attacking if you're weak. Each species has its own unique and relatable personality, you will almost feel guilty killing them.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/9784e21ae30d1db6b5e4869ae27003ff.poster.avif?t=1757251247\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/9784e21ae30d1db6b5e4869ae27003ff.webm?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/9784e21ae30d1db6b5e4869ae27003ff.mp4?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >> Bows</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With tons of shops, stats, and upgrades, you'll always find a better item... even if it is just a curse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/f5460c67f76bfe5863a6d0252b2a0143.poster.avif?t=1757251247\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/f5460c67f76bfe5863a6d0252b2a0143.webm?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/f5460c67f76bfe5863a6d0252b2a0143.mp4?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >> Curses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the story story that keeps you going, and more numbers and upgrades than you need, every run comes with its own unique goal. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/b599f9990b12951272cfd6643f27a1db.poster.avif?t=1757251247\" width=480 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/b599f9990b12951272cfd6643f27a1db.webm?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103660/extras/b599f9990b12951272cfd6643f27a1db.mp4?t=1757251247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
